    <string name="market_anu_pitch">平时比较稳，但到 deadline 周 ANU 的热度蜡烛会突然冲起来。</string>
    <string name="market_anu_trigger_1">COMP 作业堆叠带来的讨论高峰</string>
    <string name="market_anu_trigger_2">熬夜梗帖反复回流</string>
    <string name="market_anu_trigger_3">失物招领内容特别容易吃点赞</string>
    <string name="market_unsw_pitch">节奏快、回撤也快，典型 trimester 驱动型行情。</string>
    <string name="market_unsw_trigger_1">trimester 考核集中爆发</string>
    <string name="market_unsw_trigger_2">招聘会和社团宣传集中刷屏</string>
    <string name="market_unsw_trigger_3">小组作业吐槽拉高回复速度</string>
    <string name="market_usyd_pitch">点赞量高，趋势更顺，校园活动会把热度抬得很明显。</string>
    <string name="market_usyd_trigger_1">类似表白墙的内容传播很快</string>
    <string name="market_usyd_trigger_2">活动照片带来超额点赞峰值</string>
    <string name="market_usyd_trigger_3">租房和通勤帖子持续挂热榜</string>
    <string name="market_um_pitch">整体盘子更小，但跨院系梗图一来就会有很尖的上冲。</string>
    <string name="market_um_trigger_1">跨院系 meme 在午间集中放量</string>
    <string name="market_um_trigger_2">实习讨论让回复层层叠高</string>
    <string name="market_um_trigger_3">考试季问答会把尾盘波动拉大</string>

